# Cloud API keys for the *-cloud model aliases (main-cloud, coder-cloud,
# thinking-cloud, gpt4o-cloud, gemini-cloud). Populated by the ops-firstboot
# cloud-keys wizard step (not yet implemented) via SOPS decrypt. Empty is
# fine — litellm.container's EnvironmentFile= requires this path to exist
# (quadlet does not support systemd's "-/path" optional-file prefix).
